column5: Woohoo first one to report.lol Had a decent mornin,was a little cool to start out ,the young lad and I were on the water for 6am and started off,caught quite a few fish,these were some of the nicer ones.Young lad caught em all........little bugger...lol
Beautyyyyyyyyyyy Large mouth and Smallie thanks for the pics .Did the sheepshead fight more than the bass.  MTP
Great fish. Looks like a great way to kick off bass season. Thanks for the report.
THAT is awesome!!! Great start to the season! Thanks for making me drool...I cant get out today due to a relatives wedding so I wanna have as much fun as possible and might not feel too well tomorrow
that first largie is a PIG!
Ditto... that first largie is Nice! Looks like ytou also got some variety. Good job!
